column5: I took my daughter out fishing in the boat and it wasn't the best so we came back and I took 3 casts off the dock and was rewarded with this smb. Sorry about the crappy cell pic in the dark.
Nice fish dude! Tks bud, she sure was a fun guest
Nice one Geoff! Looks pretty darn long!
Nice one Geoff! Looks pretty darn long! Yeah bro she was, and wide!  I wear a 42 to 44 suit jacket and it went shoulder to shoulder (that pic didn't turn out)
